    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The head of this imposing steel *+2 greater striking vitalizing morningstar* is shaped to resemble a cluster of snarling orc faces, their sharpened tusks serving as the spikes. Forged deep in the Hold of Belkzen and wielded by elite warriors tasked with protecting their lands from the servants of the Whispering Tyrant, this brutal weapon grants void resistance 5 to any living creature who wields it.",
